title: Bach, JS - Violin Concertos - Mutter, Accardo, ECO
description:
Bach, JS: Violin Concertos in A minor and E major, Double Violin Concerto.

Johann Sebastian Bach's two Concertos for Violin and Orchestra, in A minor and E major, and his Double Concerto for Two Violins and Orchestra in D minor as performed by Anne-Sophie Mutter, Salvatore Accardo and the English Chamber Orchestra, released by EMI in 1983. Wonderful performances, perfect for those wishing to hear these works on modern instruments.

Please enjoy.
